</h2>

<div id=3D"SS1.p1" class=3D"ltx_para">
<p class=3D"ltx_p">A <span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_bold">set</span> is a=
 collection of (mathematical) objects. There is an entire
field of mathematics called set theory dedicated to the study of sets
and to their use as a foundation for mathematics, but in MATH0005 we are
going to give only an informal introduction to sets and their
properties. If you want to know more, see the further reading section at
the end of this chapter.</p>
</div>
